'''Sienar Advanced Systems''' was a company that manufactured the [[SIE-TIE twin ion engine]] system prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It was run by [[Raith Sienar/Legends|Raith Sienar]], and was a subsidiary of [[Santhe/Sienar Technologies]].

